{"word":"Gold","slug":"gold","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<b>Gold</b> Exported from:<br/> - Havilah<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=1&chapter=2&verse=12'>Gen 2:12</a> <br/> - Ophir<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=11&chapter=9&verse=28'>1Ki 9:28</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=11&chapter=10&verse=11'>1Ki 10:11</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=13&chapter=29&verse=4'>1Ch 29:4</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=14&chapter=8&verse=18'>2Ch 8:18</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=18&chapter=22&verse=24'>Job 22:24</a> <br/> - Tarshish<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=11&chapter=22&verse=48'>1Ki 22:48</a> <br/> - Parvaim<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=14&chapter=3&verse=6'>2Ch 3:6</a> <br/> - Sheba<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=11&chapter=10&verse=10'>1Ki 10:10</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=14&chapter=9&verse=9'>2Ch 9:9</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=19&chapter=72&verse=15'>Psa 72:15</a> <br/> - Uphaz<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=24&chapter=10&verse=9'>Jer 10:9</a> <br/> Refined<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=18&chapter=28&verse=19'>Job 28:19</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=18&chapter=31&verse=24'>Job 31:24</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=20&chapter=8&verse=19'>Pro 8:19</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=20&chapter=17&verse=3'>Pro 17:3</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=20&chapter=27&verse=21'>Pro 27:21</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=38&chapter=13&verse=9'>Zec 13:9</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=39&chapter=3&verse=3'>Mal 3:3</a><br/> Used in the arts:<br/> - Beaten work<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=14&chapter=9&verse=15'>2Ch 9:15</a> <br/> - Made into